QuiteRSS is RSS/Atom quite fast and comfortable to user feed reader
written on Qt/C++

Security note: QuiteRSS has known security problems and upstream appears
to have no intention of patching them or developing the program further.
But since the program is still functional on slackware and an overall
great RSS reader, I'm still leaving this SlackBuild up on SBo. Use with
care and only on trusted non-malicious feeds! Consider moving to
something else if you can.

This package won't build if qt4 is installed.
